Profile
Came Technologies is a research and development company providing new
technologies and expertise prinoipally to the meat processing sector.
Capabities
Our core business is focused on all aspects of meat quality; understanding
how muscle is converted into meat and development bechnology platforms
aimed at improved processing efficiencies and targeted meat quality
Contact
outcomes.
Our staf have specialist expertise in the fields of meat science,
biotechnology, electrical and mechanical engineering and animal welfare.
Currently, key technologies under development andlor in commercial trial
stages include:
- New Halal electrical stunning systems
- New electrical immobilisation procedures
- Smart Stimulation
- Meat Quality Modelling
- Electric Tenderometer
In the near future we will be posting information sheets on these and other
technologies currently under development.
OCame Technologies L 2000 | Ste by Back Sheep Creative
